title: “Biden” is not Biden
author: VD
content_html:
And “Fetterman” is not Fetterman. It’s not even close. I don’t care how strange or conspiratorial that sounds. The truth is right in front of your eyes. It’s literally observable.

I make no pretenses to know what’s going on or why there are suddenly so many actors playing various roles, but one thing is clear: everything about Clown World is fake and gay.
